						<p>Do you suppose if Robert III, Walter, Alexander, or the Duke of Albany were known to us in daguerreotype rather'n the marginal doodlings of the avowedly unfucked, we'd judge them finer than the wounded and questionably alimented specimen above? A handsome aspiring king of gloom is like a chocolate-dipped bologna sandwich --and while that might've been the sort of thing Poe ate, by the looks of those sickly jowls, it's still an abomination. Like my similie.</p>
