										<li id="comment-151896" class="adminbody"><div class="adminhead"><img alt='Mircea Popescu`s avatar' src='http://trilema.com/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">2</div>
